HEADWORD: Toxicology
<hw>Tox`i*col"o*gy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>toxiko`n</grk> poison + <ets>-logy</ets>; cf. F.
<ets>toxicologie</ets>. See <er>Toxic</er>. ]</ety> <def>The science
which treats of poisons, their effects, antidotes, and recognition;
also, a discourse or treatise on the science.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

